PrecisLEAST DEVELOPED DEVELOPING COUNTRIES ORDER (CAMBODIA, LIBERIA, MADAGASCAR, MOZAMBIQUE, SOLOMON ISLANDS, ZAIRE AND ZAMBIA) - which designates these countries as "least developed developing countries" and extends the benefit of free rates of customs duty to all goods that originate there.

LEAST DEVELOPED DEVELOPING COUNTRIES ORDER (CAMBODIA, LIBERIA, MADAGASCAR,
MOZAMBIQUE, SOLOMON ISLANDS, ZAIRE AND ZAMBIA) - which designates these
